[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0322","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0727","title":"OpenBSD 内核 IPsec 数据包未加密发送漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 内核存在资源泄漏漏洞，该漏洞导致 IPsec 安全协议的加密机制失效，使得本应加密传输的 IPsec 数据包能够以明文形式未经加密直接发送。攻击者可利用此漏洞绕过 IPsec 提供的数据传输加密保护，截获或监听本应受保护的网络通信内容，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响运行 OpenBSD 系统且启用 IPsec 功能的设备，攻击条件为攻击者需位于网络传输路径上以截获未加密的数据包。OpenBSD 已在后续版本中修复此内核泄漏问题，建议用户及时升级系统版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0727"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.840","remediation":"升级至 OpenBSD 2.6 及以上版本，该版本修复了内核中 IPsec 处理流程的内存泄漏问题，确保所有 IPsec 数据包均被正确加密后发送。若无法升级，可临时禁用 IPsec 功能或使用 pf 防火墙限制相关流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6127","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0f25967d744704fe14324ac10f2b57e945aed081/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d2eb55660fa7a900eec90103b031be5d6f98d9ec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0727","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/370723f19bf3029ced147d3128d845761f3168c3/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-07xx/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/7ad5a0b8a6cc847a756fff84ffda27203e470e86/1999/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/490d6657aaeb62053fddc3213da299eb1e656f38/api/1999/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0727.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0727.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0239","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0682","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 邮件中继绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 存在邮件中继绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可通过封装 SMTP 地址的方式绕过反中继功能限制，利用该服务器转发垃圾邮件，导致服务器被滥用为垃圾邮件中继站。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0682"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1999-08-06","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"应用 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-027 提供的补丁，或升级到不再受此漏洞影响的 Exchange 版本。由于 Exchange 5.5 已停止支持，建议迁移到受支持的 Exchange 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T17:45:47.329891126+00:00","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-027","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237927","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/567"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0319","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0719","title":"Gnumeric Guile 插件代码执行漏洞","description":"Gnumeric 电子表格软件中的 Guile 插件存在代码执行漏洞。攻击者可通过诱使用户打开特制的恶意电子表格文件，利用 Guile 脚本扩展功能执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Gnumeric 的早期版本，攻击者需要本地访问权限或诱导用户下载并打开恶意文件，CVSS v2.0 评分为 4.6，可导致机密性、完整性和可用性部分受损。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0719"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.830","remediation":"升级 Gnumeric 至 1.2.x 以上版本，该漏洞在后续版本中已修复 Guile 插件对 Scheme 代码的沙箱逃逸问题。如无法升级，可移除或禁用 gnumeric-guile 插件包（如 Debian/Ubuntu 中执行 apt-get remove gnumeric-guile），或限制 Guile 插件仅加载受信任的 Scheme 脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/563"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1300","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1300.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0913","title":"Network Security Wizards Dragon-Fire IDS 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Dragon-Fire IDS 1.0 版本的 Web 管理接口包含不安全的 CGI 脚本 dfire.cgi，攻击者可通过该脚本中的 IPONE 字段以管道符（|）为前缀注入系统命令，实现远程命令执行。攻击者无需认证即可在目标系统上以 nobody 用户权限执行任意命令，可能导致系统被完全控制。该漏洞无需特殊工具即可利用，危害极大。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0913"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-05","updated":"1999-08-05","remediation":"该漏洞为 1999 年的古老产品，厂商 Network Security Wizards 早已停止支持，无官方补丁可用。建议立即停用 Dragon-Fire IDS 并替换为现代 IDS 产品（如 Snort 或 Suricata）；如无法立即替换，须在 Web 服务器层面通过 .htaccess 或防火墙规则限制对 dfire.cgi 的访问来源 IP，并移除公网暴露的 Dragon-Fire 管理页面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93383593909438&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/564","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19444","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/94380d498cb52b65d051c9bd443b6f2aa85bf8ec/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0913.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1300.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0285","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0703","title":"OpenBSD/BSDI等多款Unix操作系统设备文件标志设置漏洞","description":"OpenBSD、BSDI 及其他类 Unix 操作系统中，普通用户可对字符设备和块设备调用 chflags 及 fchflags 系统调用来修改文件标志位。该漏洞源于内核未对设备特殊文件的标志修改操作进行充分的权限检查，导致低权限用户能够更改设备文件的不可变标志（如 schg、sappnd），从而绕过系统安全策略。攻击者利用此漏洞可修改关键设备文件的保护属性，进而实现文件篡改或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD、BSDI 等多款 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 3.6，危害等级低，攻击需本地用户权限。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0703"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.917","remediation":"升级 OpenBSD 至 2.5 或更高版本，BSDI 升级至 4.0.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在对应版本的内核中修复了对字符设备和块设备的 chflags/fchflags 权限检查。如无法升级，可通过限制用户对 /dev 目录下设备文件的写入权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-066.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e927b0fe51353a8ed03f0466aad3c47ffd172da3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0703","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0703.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/8c57fab4f71bd6fdcec1202e5361e2a9805c4950/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r2hm-7w9p-5qrc/GHSA-r2hm-7w9p-5qrc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0703.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--397c3002-48f0-4b72-a230-03cbb311dac0.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000716.txt","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0224","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0224.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0677","title":"Ramp Networks WebRamp 默认口令漏洞","description":"WebRamp 200i 及 M3 设备的 Web 管理接口存在默认弱口令。攻击者可通过网络访问设备管理页面，使用出厂默认用户名和密码登录，从而获取设备完全控制权限，包括修改网络配置、查看敏感信息等。该漏洞影响 WebRamp 200i 和 M3 系列产品，可通过网络远程利用，危害等级为高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0677"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1999-08-03","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即登录 WebRamp Web 管理界面修改默认管理员密码，禁止继续使用空密码或出厂预设口令。通过防火墙或访问控制列表限制管理端口（通常为 TCP 80/443）的访问来源，仅允许受信任管理网段连接。该产品年代久远且已停止维护，若仍在生产环境中使用，应尽快隔离管理面并替换为具备强认证与可更新固件的现代网络设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0677","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e4e2425598fefb3de3071f42b9b8bdfa153b170/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0677.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f7dca00abc08334092ecb772a8cf4381abbc2a48/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrgh-ph38-f973/GHSA-mrgh-ph38-f973.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0677.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/577/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0224.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0224.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0204","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0671","title":"ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 CWD 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 FTP 客户端在处理 CWD（切换工作目录）命令时，未对用户输入的目录路径长度进行充分边界检查，导致栈缓冲区溢出。攻击者可通过构造超长的 CWD 命令参数，覆盖函数返回地址，从而在客户端系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞属于客户端侧漏洞，利用方式为远程攻击，攻击者需诱骗用户连接到恶意 FTP 服务器或访问恶意 FTP 站点触发溢出。成功利用后可导致客户端进程被控制，机密性、完整性和可用性均可能受损。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0671"],"sources":["cve","nvd"],"published":"1999-08-03","updated":"1999-08-03","remediation":"NextFTP 已停止维护且无官方补丁，强烈建议更换为当前受支持的 FTP 客户端软件（如 FileZilla、WinSCP 等）。若短期内无法迁移，应避免使用该软件连接不受信任的 FTP 服务器，并在防火墙中限制其对外网络访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T15:28:59Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/572"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0211","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0672","title":"Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7 IRC 客户端 Topic 字段远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端 1.0 beta7R 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，源于程序在处理 IRC 频道主题（TOPIC）消息时，未对服务器返回的主题字符串长度进行充分校验，导致超长数据覆盖相邻内存区域。攻击者通过控制 IRC 服务器或在用户加入频道时发送构造的超长主题内容，可触发缓冲区溢出，进而可能实现远程代码执行或导致客户端崩溃。该漏洞影响运行 Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 的所有 Windows 用户，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中等。用户应升级至更新版本以修复此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0672"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.990","remediation":"建议停止使用 Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R，该版本已不再维护且无官方补丁，应迁移至目前仍在维护的 IRC 客户端（如 HexChat、irssi 或 WeeChat）以彻底消除此缓冲区溢出风险。临时缓解措施：不要加入包含超长或不可信 channel topic 的 IRC 频道，并在防火墙中限制客户端对外连接至仅信任的 IRC 服务器地址。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/573","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19449","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fb6d88d74424546f8735bb570a195f07b71e3801/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0672","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0672.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/512c773c61886081b2589de76a8cfde795349819/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/307.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.223","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1053","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1053.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1337","title":"Midnight Commander FTP客户端历史文件敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"Midnight Commander（mc）4.5.11 之前版本的 FTP 客户端存在敏感信息泄露漏洞。该客户端在访问 FTP 站点后，会将用户名和密码以明文形式存储于全局可读的历史记录文件中，导致本地其他用户可读取该文件获取凭证信息，进而实现权限提升。攻击者只需具备本地普通用户权限即可利用此漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1337"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Midnight Commander 4.5.11 或更高版本，该版本已修复密码明文存储问题。如无法升级，立即执行 chmod 600 ~/.mc/history 限制历史文件权限为仅当前用户可读写，并删除该文件中已保存的明文密码条目。建议使用 .netrc 文件替代自动保存密码功能，并定期检查历史文件是否包含敏感信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93370073207984&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/9873.php","http://www.osvdb.org/5921","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1337"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1053.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1014","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1227","title":"Ethereal 数据包捕获文件符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Ethereal（Wireshark 前身）存在不安全的临时文件处理漏洞，本地攻击者可利用符号链接攻击，在目标系统上诱使 Ethereal 将捕获的数据包写入任意文件，覆盖系统敏感文件。该漏洞影响早期版本 Ethereal，攻击者须拥有本地账户权限方可利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1227"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.377","remediation":"升级 Ethereal 至 0.10.13 及以上版本（或迁移至 Wireshark 1.0+），这些版本已修复符号链接跟随问题。临时缓解措施：避免以 root 权限运行数据包分析工具，并在保存捕获文件前使用 `umask 077` 限制文件权限，防止本地低权限用户通过符号链接覆盖敏感文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00126.html","http://www.ethereal.com/lists/ethereal-dev/199907/msg00130.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3334","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1227","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1227.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h/GHSA-fx42-9wp5-842h.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87548/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1227.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000713.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1014.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0972","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1130","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server JHTML 源代码泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1 及 3.6 版本默认配置存在信息泄露漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向搜索功能发送特制的 HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat 模式文件请求，读取服务器上 JHTML 文件的源代码。该漏洞源于搜索引擎默认配置不当，导致敏感源码暴露，攻击者可从中获取数据库连接信息、业务逻辑等敏感数据，为后续攻击提供跳板。影响范围包括 Netscape Enterprise Server 3.5.1 及可能的相关版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1130"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:47.070","remediation":"Netscape Enterprise Server 已停止维护且不再提供安全更新，建议立即迁移至受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache HTTP Server 或 Nginx）。如无法迁移，可删除或重命名默认搜索规则文件 HTML-tocrec-demo1.pat 以阻止源码泄露，同时限制对服务器 JHTML 目录的访问权限。长期方案应彻底停用该产品并迁移数据。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93346448121208&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93337389603117&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/559","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19443","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1130.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1130","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1130.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1130.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ghc8-6pj7-h897/GHSA-ghc8-6pj7-h897.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1130.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000712.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a45f29c3-4e79-4dd6-bbc1-b2c3fc3ea87a.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0972.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0972.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0240","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0683","title":"Network Associates Gauntlet 防火墙 5.0 畸形 ICMP 报文拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 在处理 ICMP 数据包时存在缺陷，未能对畸形的 ICMP 报文进行正确校验。远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向目标防火墙发送构造异常的 ICMP 数据包，即可触发该漏洞导致防火墙服务崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务（DoS）。该漏洞影响运行 Gauntlet Firewall 5.0 版本的设备，攻击条件仅需攻击者能够向目标防火墙发送网络数据包，利用方式简单，可直接通过普通网络访问发起，威胁网络边界防护的可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0683"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-30","updated":"2026-07-17","remediation":"建议升级 Network Associates Gauntlet Firewall 至 5.0 后续补丁版本或更高版本，并在防火墙策略中配置 ICMP 包过滤规则，阻断来源不明的畸形 ICMP 报文。如暂时无法升级，可在边界路由器上配置 ACL，仅允许必要 ICMP 类型通过，丢弃异常 ICMP 包以缓解拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1029","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/556","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19441","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4ff02bbc729aaafe393c2c43802fb087571bc1bf/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0683.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0240.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0240.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0492","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0770","title":"Check Point Firewall-1 防火墙表饱和拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Check Point Firewall-1 防火墙在处理以 ACK 或其他非 SYN 数据包开始的连接时设置了过长的超时时间，攻击者可通过向无响应系统发起大量连接尝试耗尽连接表资源，导致防火墙拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Check Point Firewall-1 3.0 和 4.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程发起大量伪造连接请求耗尽连接表资源，导致防火墙无法处理合法连接请求，造成拒绝服务。CVSS 评分 2.1，属于低危级别拒绝服务漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0770"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.327","remediation":"升级 Check Point Firewall-1 至 4.1 SP2 或更高版本，并在防火墙策略中将非 SYN 包连接超时时间从默认值调低至 10 秒以内，或在边界路由器配置 ACL 丢弃非 SYN 首包的新建连接尝试作为临时缓解措施","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1027","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19436","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0770.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0770","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0770.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/70f84d5684ed60f7a4d0750993d15c30e4fe3bbf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0770.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cmfr-w36g-hm8h/GHSA-cmfr-w36g-hm8h.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/stream.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0770.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000710.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0492.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0276","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0276.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0700","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16406,\"outputTokens\":36,\"totalTokens\":16442}}","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 系统中的电话拨号程序（dialer.exe）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当攻击者在 dialer.ini 拨号配置文件中写入格式错误的拨号条目时，可触发 dialer.exe 的缓冲区溢出，进而在目标系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP 1 至 SP 5 的所有版本，攻击者需要具备在本地系统上修改或创建恶意 dialer.ini 文件的能力，通常通过社会工程学手段诱导用户打开特制拨号文件或替换配置文件实现利用。成功利用该漏洞的攻击者可获得与拨号程序相同的系统权限，对受影响系统造成严重安全威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0700"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-07-29T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.550","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 1999 年 11 月发布的安全公告 MS99-048 对应补丁（适用于 Windows NT 4.0 各 SP 版本），通过 Windows Update 或微软官网下载更新。如暂无法打补丁，可在组策略中限制普通用户对 dialer.ini 文件的写入权限，并禁止用户打开来源不明的拨号配置文件作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237185","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-026","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19440","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8b4df384387a55d60e5ec37568fb4254388bef40/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0700","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0700.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/30f77465b94d71209b45a239e791a1fe062c9e8b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f4cf158806845cf97767a48ffe8073c2008dffff/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-256c-v65p-vvfh/GHSA-256c-v65p-vvfh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--9d37c81c-28be-4e85-a09d-7f39454834f2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0276.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0924","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0924.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1078","title":"Ipswitch WS_FTP Pro 6.0 ws_ftp.ini 配置文件口令弱加密漏洞","description":"WS_FTP Pro 6.0 在初始化文件 ws_ftp.ini 中使用弱加密算法存储用户口令，攻击者可通过网络获取该文件后轻易解密口令，导致敏感信息泄露和系统权限被非法获取。该漏洞利用难度低，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1078"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-29","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Ipswitch 已针对该漏洞发布安全更新，建议用户升级到 WS_FTP Pro 更高版本；对于已停止支持的版本，建议迁移至其他受安全维护的 FTP 客户端软件，并避免在配置文件中存储明文或弱加密口令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:32:23.199804110+00:00","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/547","http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9907&L=ntbugtraq&D=0&P=10370&F=P"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0924.toml"}]